---
layout: base
title: Contact
description: How to reach The Freethinking Times — tips, corrections, submissions, and general inquiries.
permalink: /contact/
---

<div class="container" style="padding-top: var(--space-10); padding-bottom: var(--space-20);">
  <div class="container--prose">

    <header style="margin-bottom: var(--space-10); padding-bottom: var(--space-6); border-bottom: 3px solid var(--color-ink);">
      <h1 style="font-family: var(--font-masthead); font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 5vw, 3.815rem); margin-bottom: var(--space-4);">Contact</h1>
      <p style="font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: var(--text-lg); color: var(--color-ink-muted); line-height: var(--leading-loose); max-width: 60ch;">
        We read every message. Here is how to reach us.
      </p>
    </header>

    <div class="article-body">

      <h2>General inquiries</h2>
      <p>For questions, comments, or feedback:</p>
      <p style="margin: var(--space-4) 0;">
        <a href="mailto:{{ site.email }}" style="font-family: var(--font-ui); font-weight: 600; font-size: var(--text-md);">{{ site.email }}</a>
      </p>

      <h2>Suggest a correction</h2>
      <p>If you have found an error in any article or library text, please email us at <a href="mailto:{{ site.email }}?subject=Correction">{{ site.email }}</a> with:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>The URL or title of the article</li>
        <li>What the error is</li>
        <li>What the correct information should be</li>
      </ul>
      <p>All corrections are published in our <a href="/corrections/">corrections log</a> and noted on the article itself.</p>

      <h2>Submit a piece</h2>
      <p>We accept submissions from outside contributors. See our <a href="/submit/">submissions page</a> for guidelines, topics of interest, and how to pitch.</p>

      <h2>Newsletter</h2>
      <p>Get new articles by email. Free, always. Unsubscribe at any time.</p>
      <div style="max-width: 400px; margin: var(--space-4) 0;">
        {% set subscribeVariant = "inline" %}
        {% include "partials/subscribe.njk" %}
      </div>

      <h2>RSS</h2>
      <p>Follow via your preferred feed reader:</p>
      <p><a href="/feed.xml" style="font-family: var(--font-ui); font-weight: 600;">{{ site.url }}/feed.xml</a></p>

      <h2>Support</h2>
      <p>{{ site.title }} is independent and reader-supported. If this work matters to you, consider <a href="/support/">supporting us</a>.</p>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>
